  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## UPDATE\r\n\r\nFor now, we only should show the `[Alicia] is now a contact` message both for sender and receiver of CR after the CR approval. \r\n\r\nDesign: https://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1694%3A380446&t=53g6tG6gOO7nUzqh-1\r\n\r\n<img width=\"366\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-06-13 at 12 56 52\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/67952253/acaf9d62-7604-41d5-b410-d336d44e1339\">\r\n\r\nAdditional requirement:\r\n\r\n> Contact request card and \"You sent a contact request to...\" message should not appear in the conversation, only in notification center, so we can hide/delete from here\r\n\r\n---\r\nThree scenarios where new systems messages are needed:\r\n\r\n#### 1. Alice sends CR to Bob for the first time\r\n\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=1694%3A380446&t=53g6tG6gOO7nUzqh-1\r\n\r\n1. Bob receives a notification in AC\r\n2. 1-1 chat is NOT opened for both users\r\n3. Bob accepts CR\r\n4. 1-1 chat is created for Bob and Alice\r\n5. Alice can see her message sent with CR and the system message “Bob now is a contact”\r\n6. Bob can see Alice’s message received with CR and \r\n\r\n#### 2. Bob removes Alice from contacts \r\n\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/7KIYbhoqNGAIFonE0w9TDz/Messages-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=5611-457496&t=JAqbuAHD9cHrgUm7-4\r\n\r\n1. The input field is disabled in the chat for Bob and Alice\r\n2. Alice can see “Add Bob as a contact to send message” in place of the input field (this will be a clickable button) and the system message “Bob removed you as a contact”\r\n3. Bob can see “Add Alice as a contact to send message” in place of the input field (this will be a clickable button) and the system message “Alice removed as a contact”\r\n\r\n#### 3. Alice sends another CR to Bob\r\n\r\n1. Bob receives a notification in AC\r\n2. 1-1 chat is opened for both users BEFORE the CR is accepted\r\n3. Bob can open chat and accept/reject CR inside the chat (there will be corresponding buttons)\r\n4. Bob can see the system message “Alice sent you a contact request” and the message received with CR from Alice below it\r\n5. Alice can see the system message “You sent a contact request to Bob” and the message sent with CR to Bob below it",
